ZH: 他的眼界很狭窄，对世界的了解非常有限。
EN: His perspective is very narrow, and his understanding of the world is very limited.

ZH: 我们应该开阔自己的眼界，接触更多不同文化。
EN: We should broaden our horizons and expose ourselves to different cultures.

ZH: 旅行可以拓宽你的眼界，让你对不同地方有更深入的了解。
EN: Traveling can broaden your horizons and give you a deeper understanding of different places.

ZH: 他从小就接触到各种各样的音乐，所以他的音乐眼界非常开阔。
EN: He has been exposed to various kinds of music since he was young, so his musical horizons are very broad.

ZH: 学习新的语言可以拓宽你的眼界，使你能够与更多人交流。
EN: Learning a new language can broaden your horizons and allow you to communicate with more people.

ZH: 他通过阅读大量的书籍扩展了自己的眼界。
EN: He expanded his horizons by reading a lot of books.

ZH: 这次展览会让我对当代艺术有了全新的眼界。
EN: This exhibition gave me a whole new perspective on contemporary art.

ZH: 长时间待在一个地方容易限制你的眼界。
EN: Staying in one place for a long time can easily limit your perspective.

ZH: 通过参加各种活动，他不断扩大自己的眼界。
EN: By participating in various activities, he constantly expands his horizons.

ZH: 遇到不同的人和事可以让你的眼界变得更加开阔。
EN: Meeting different people and experiencing different things can make your perspective more open-minded.

ZH: 他的眼界受到了教育的局限，缺乏真正的实践经验。
EN: His perspective is limited by education and lacks real-life experience.

ZH: 观看纪录片是一种开拓眼界的方式。
EN: Watching documentaries is a way to broaden one's horizons.

ZH: 去一个不同的国家旅行可以让你对其他文化有全新的眼界。
EN: Traveling to a different country can give you a whole new perspective on other cultures.

ZH: 参加一些国际交流活动可以让你拓宽眼界。
EN: Participating in international exchange activities can broaden your horizons.

ZH: 他希望通过进修学习来开阔自己的眼界。
EN: He hopes to broaden his horizons through further education.

ZH: 阅读各种不同类型的书籍可以帮助你拓展眼界。
EN: Reading books of different genres can help you expand your horizons.

ZH: 跟不同领域的人交流可以丰富你的眼界。
EN: Communicating with people from different fields can enrich your perspective.

ZH: 旅游是一种开阔眼界的好方法。
EN: Traveling is a great way to broaden your horizons.

ZH: 长时间待在一个固定的环境中容易限制我们的眼界。
EN: Staying in a fixed environment for a long time can easily limit our perspectives.

ZH: 了解不同的观点可以帮助我们扩大眼界。
EN: Understanding different viewpoints can help us broaden our horizons.
